de.dfki.embots.bml.lex
Class BehaviorLexicon

java.lang.Object
  de.dfki.embots.bml.lex.BehaviorLexicon

public class BehaviorLexicon
extends java.lang.Object

The behavior lexicon stores templates for a given lexeme. The main idea for having this in a separate class is to store variants of the same "lexeme" under the same token.
